<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.7.8">
<l>muṟṟilum paiṅkiḷiyum pantumūcalum pēcukiṉṟa</l>
<l>ciṟṟilmeṉ pūvaiyumviṭ ṭakaṉṟaceḻuṅ kōtaitaṉṉai,</l>
<l>peṟṟilēṉ muṟṟiḻaiyaip piṟappilipiṉ ṉēnaṭantu</l>
<l>maṟṟellām  kaitoḻappōy vayalālipu kuvarkolō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I do not have her [with] thick garlands and abounding in jewels</l>
<l rend="indent">who has [now] departed</l>
<l>Leaving her [toy] winnowing fan, green parakeet, ball, swing,</l>
<l rend="indent">and her soft myna bird which chatters in [its] cage;</l>
<l>As she walks behind the birthless [one],</l>
<l rend="indent">are they setting out for Āli of the paddy fields</l>
<l>Going as all the others worship, hands [joined]?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
